text: Catwings Return is the second book in a series of four American children's picture books written by Ursula K. Le Guin. S. D. Schindler made the pictures. Scholastic published the book in 1989. It tells the stories of kittens who were born with wings. Category:American children's books Category:Books by Ursula K. Le Guin Category:1989 books
title: Catwings Return
